title: Chris_Brown-Royalty_(Deluxe_Edition)-(2015)
description:
R&B artist Chris Brown will release his seventh album, Royalty. The album is produced by Boi-1da, Vinylz, The MeKanics, Afrojack, Blaqtuxedo, and more ... It features Future on the deluxe edition, Tayla Parx and rapper Solo Lucci on the promotional single "Wrist". The album lead single is "Liquor", after that Breezy has released few singles "Zero, "Back To Sleep" and "Find By Me". Please support the artist and buy his new album!
